nk you, Matteo."],[2456,2612,"Rest well, Amber."],[2668,2760,"See you soon."],[2824,2948,"I'll see you soon."],[4120,4364,"It's time to forget all of this."],[5164,5252,"Who is it?"],[5972,6076,"You're not welcome here."],[7016,7180,"Sergei, let me go!"],[7368,7536,"What's with you and that Italian guy?"],[7552,7652,"We're just friends."],[7652,7736,"He helped me."],[7736,7824,"Oh, friends."],[7840,7960,"Yeah, I know that look."],[7976,8148,"He wants more than friendship, Amber."]],"44":[[16,136,"Why would you care?"],[164,308,"My personal life is none of your business."],[308,456,"It is my business!"],[496,624,"Why did you stand me up?"],[696,784,"Why did you run off?"],[784,892,"What was I supposed to do?"],[892,1180,"Just stay and watch you screw your ex-wife?"],[1448,1552,"What did you see?"],[1584,1656,"Enough."],[1700,2120,"I saw and heard more than I ever wanted to."],[2120,2284,"You can't listen to Sonia, Amber."],[2284,2456,"She lies about everything."],[2456,2540,"You want me to repeat"],[2540,2744,"every nasty things she said about me?"],[2744,2888,"Look, I know that you're mad."],[2956,3024,"Let me explain."],[3024,3148,"I’m not angry."],[3252,3376,"Why should I be?"],[3464,3692,"It was just sex between us. Nothing more."],[4444,4560,"Just sex?"],[4692,4796,"Just sex?!"],[4828,4924,"No strings attached."],[4924,5080,"So why should I care?"],[5392,5500,"You are telling me"],[5500,5672,"that everything we've been through,"],[5672,5836,"you don't feel anything for me?"],[6260,6456,"Do I have to spell it out for you?"],[6456,6864,"You mean nothing to me, Sergei."],[7180,7308,"I know how I felt."],[7428,7588,"And I know you felt it, too."],[7744,7936,"It wasn't just physical, Amber."],[7992,8100,"And, you know it."],[8192,8676,"Every single trick he used in bed."],[8716,9100,"Every position he ever tried on you..."],[9160,9328,"I taught him."],[9664,9752,"No!"],[9868,10060,"You stay away from me."],[10276,10468,"Just thinking about you touching me"],[10468,10