r, right now!"],[5656,5860,"Touch her again and I'll chop them off!"],[5860,6048,"What the hell are you doing here?"],[6160,6328,"Are you trying to threaten me?"],[6412,6600,"I am the commanding officer!"],[6976,7076,"Are you crazy?"],[7152,7300,"Slapping your superior!"],[7316,7420,"As of tonight,"],[7600,7708,"you're retired."],[7744,7852,"What do you mean?"],[7888,7968,"You?"],[8040,8228,"You are the new commander?"],[8704,8792,"Amber."],[9700,9860,"I ever see you in Moscow again,"],[9940,10088,"I will kill you."],[10324,10432,"Take care of him."]],"52":[[36,192,"Mom, you're amazing!"],[200,376,"I can't believe that Italian jerk"],[376,588,"was working with you all alone!"],[588,888,"That tramp got what she deserved."],[888,1144,"Now the General is mine."],[1692,1788,"Dad."],[2048,2272,"Why are you still with the slut?"],[2272,2456,"Sergei, don't be fooled again."],[2484,2760,"This bitch slept with the Navy Commander!"],[2848,2920,"Sonia."],[3028,3180,"How did you know that she was with him?"],[3284,3452,"Was this your plan all along?"],[3556,3768,"Is that what this is your plan all along?"],[3768,4052,"I don't know what you're talking about."],[4500,4660,"We found this contract on Matteo."],[5164,5220,"Dad..."],[5296,5372,"Please."],[5464,5528,"Be calm."],[5528,5668,"You are no son of my."],[5696,5868,"I should remove you from the inheritance."],[5868,5956,"What?"],[5996,6056,"No!"],[6064,6220,"Shut your goddamn mouth!"],[6340,6496,"You worthless bastard!"],[6564,6716,"I should throw you in jail!"],[6756,6840,"Don't you think I know that"],[6840,7024,"you framed Amber for theft?"],[7072,7284,"Sergei, you can't be serious!"],[7284,7608,"You won’t put your own son in prison!"],[7636,7744,"Not just him!"],[7764,7848,"You!"]],"53":[[36,128,"Drugging me,"],[128,352,"conspiring with that businessman,"],[352,480,"bribing the commander."],[548,740,"Your crimes are worse than his!"],[892,1132,"I'm not going anywhere, you son of a bitch!"],[1212,1344,"Shut your mouth!"],[